    random_uuid = uuid4()
    return await self.meross_manager.async_execute_cmd(destination_device_uuid
        =str(random_uuid), method='GET', namespace=Namespace.SYSTEM_ALL,

with self.assertRaises(CommandTimeoutError):
    await send_command_to_unknown_device()
